Ported crates (copied with modifications):
  dynamo-tokens/        — Token management, PositionalLineageHash, PositionalRadixTree
  dynamo-memory/        — Memory utilities
  dynamo-kv-hashing/    — KV cache hash computation
  dynamo-kv-router/     — KV-aware request routing with radix tree indexing
  dynamo-runtime/       — Runtime configuration and transport abstractions
  kvbm-common/          — Shared KVBM types
  kvbm-config/          — KVBM configuration
  kvbm-consolidator/    — KV event consolidation
  kvbm-engine/          — KVBM engine (leader/worker coordination)
  kvbm-kernels/         — KVBM CUDA kernels
  kvbm-logical/         — Core block lifecycle management (type-safe state machine,
                          registry, pool system, event pipeline, block manager)
  kvbm-physical/        — Physical block layout and transfer management

